<L>__{exterior ridgemont bleachers night}
<A>__{the ridgemont football bleachers are full of cheering students. we see the same basic groups from lunch court, and many more. the cheerleaders are on the field cindy carr, dina phillips and company and their cheerleader "husbands" sit directly in front of them in the stands. linda and stacy sit in the bleachers with some of the swenson's girls. the rat and damone sit several rows above them, watching. the teachers sit together in another section.}
